Sumner Getchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sumner_Getchell 0 Sumner Getchell (October 20, 1906 – September 21, 1990) was an American film actor. He appeared in 65 films between 1926 and 1953. He was born in Oakland, California and died in Sebastopol, California. Sumner_Getchell ( October_20_,_1906 – September_21_,_1990 ) was an_American_film_actor .
